## üåø Branch Creation Workflow

### Step 1: Get to Clean State
```bash
# Switch to main branch
git checkout main

# Pull latest changes
git pull origin main
```

### Step 2: Create New Branch with Conventional Name
```bash
git checkout -b [type]/[description]
```

